### Test Tenant Resolution Middleware

# Test 1: Request WITHOUT X-Tenant-Id header (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:5036/api/v1/tenant/info

###

# Test 2: Request with INVALID X-Tenant-Id header (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:5036/api/v1/tenant/info
X-Tenant-Id: invalid-guid

###

# Test 3: Request with VALID X-Tenant-Id header (should return 200)
GET http://localhost:5036/api/v1/tenant/info
X-Tenant-Id: 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

###

# Test 4: Swagger endpoint (should bypass tenant check)
GET http://localhost:5036/swagger/index.html
